#: ../../Introduction/Introduction.rst:223
msgid "Introduction to Surface Water Treatment"
msgstr ""

#: ../../Introduction/Introduction.rst:225
msgid ""
"We treat water because it doesn't meet the requirements for its intended "
"use. We need to understand the problem so that we can understand existing"
