"separation of particles from water that we would like to use it to remove"
" small particles too. Unfortunately, gravity becomes rather ineffective "
"at separating pathogens and small inorganic particles such as clay. The "
"terminal velocities (:eq:`eq_laminar_terminal_velocity`) of these "
